OL,5,Csales'
OL,6, Leading garden retailers are still
OL,7, failing to stop the sale of peat in
OL,8, compost despite pressure from the
OL,9, government and campaigners.
OL,11,FThe Wildlife Trusts said only one of 20
OL,12,Fretailers contacted said it would
OL,13,Feliminate peat from its shelves this
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FThe restoration of peatlands is a key
OL,17,Fpart of the government's strategy to
OL,18,Fmitigate the impact of climate change.
OL,20,FHighly absorbent, it also helps with
OL,21,Fflood prevention.
